com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.CartographicSupport, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.IPrintable, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.IFillSymbol, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.ISymbol, com.iver.utiles.IPersistence
public class DotDensityFillSymbol
extends com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.AbstractFillSymbol

Symbol that draws a set of points within a polygon. The amount of points is defined by the field dotCount.

This symbol only draws the points. The outline and the fill of the polygon is handled by a SimpleFillSymboll where a DotDensityFillSymbol should be embedded.

Author:
jaume dominguez faus - jaume.dominguez@iver.es
